messages.message: Yes that would be amazing!!! I was thinking similarly about the proto generated files
are you thinking (a) auto-generate and auto-check in (in CI), or (b) auto-generate as needed and never check-in?

let’s chat before we decide to do it for proto generated files (at least in Python)

in Python, proto builds take up ~15 seconds for every “make build” if you don’t check things in — so would prefer not to go back to that world
I've noticed that too. Hence I think (a) would be preferable to (b)
